# parallel Builds
##    Jenkins Pipeline -Parallel Build & Test
you will learn how to **run build and test in paraler**

pipeline {
    agent any 
    stages{
        stage ('Paraller Tasks')
            parallel {
                stage('Build') {
                    steps {
                        sh 'mn clean compile'
                    }
                }
                stage('Test') {
                    steps {
                        sh 'mvn test'
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

